Spring blood pressure screenings are here! 🌼

How would you tell a Spanish-speaking patient that you are going to take their blood pressure?

Follow along as Nurse Cookie (@cookiegirlrn) teaches us a few basic Spanish phrases to better assist Spanish-speaking patients. Because better communication means better care! 🩺

📩 Be sure to SEND this video to one other nurse who can use this information.

¡Adios, for now, nurses!
